Class Controller

java.lang.Object
Controller
public class Controller
extends java.lang.Object
Controller class handles the bulk of the program and communicates between the Model and the View of the program and their respective subclasses. Most of the methods are event handlers and getters to set the event handlers for the items in View and its subclasses.

Author:
Malachi Parks
